    "description": "Nucleus Software International Enterprises, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Senior Software Engineer for our Ludhiana operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Nucleus Software International Enterprises:\nNucleus Software International Enterprises is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in Java\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in REST APIs\n• Proficiency in Rust\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Referral bonus program\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ludhiana, Punjab, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Nucleus Software International Enterprises!",
